Description: MySQL/MariaDB backup and restore desktop app
 DBack connects to remote Linux servers or WordPress sites, streams database
 dumps to local files with compression, and restores backups to any saved host.
 Hosts, templates, history, and logs live in an encrypted local vault.
 Built with Go and Gio.
